"cypher" : "MATCH (g:Gene)
WHERE toLower(g.displayName) = toLower('BRCA1')
OPTIONAL MATCH (g)<-[:ProteinEncodedByGene]-(p:Protein)-[:ProteinExpressedInTissue]->(t:Tissue)
OPTIONAL MATCH (g)-[r:GeneAssociatedWithDisorder]->(dis:Disorder)
WHERE r.scoreOpenTargets IS NULL OR r.scoreOpenTargets > 0.3
RETURN g.primaryDomainId AS geneId
